 "prompt": "A sleek, matte black insulated puffer jacket with subtle stitched lines and a modern silhouette, A minimalist, luxuriously textured apartment lounge with soft, warm ambient light, A stylish East Asian male, late 20s, with a modern short haircut, Close-up of male hand gently stroking the jacket's matte fabric, emphasizing its soft texture and subtle volume, Rembrandt lighting, Phase One IQ4, 8k, hyper-realistic --no text, logo",
 "styling": { "style": "tactile close-up", "color": "muted tones", "lighting": "soft, directional" }
}
```
